snippet.title: Johnny Depp Is Not The Victim! (The McTaggart Attack Podcast)
snippet.description:
In this episode of the McTaggart Attack Podcast I explain why I think Johnny Depp is not the victim regarding his legal issues with ex wife Amber Heard.

Here are the 2 articles I was talking about:

https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/features/hes-radioactive-inside-johnny-depps-self-made-implosion

https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54506759
